lead_paragraph: American 18th seed John Isner ended the Wimbledon odyssey of Australian qualifier Matthew Barton on Friday, serving his way to victory 7-6(8) 7-6(3) 7-6(8) in a high-octane second-round clash.

headline.print_headline: Isner Ends Outsider Barton's Wimbledon Odyssey
